---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead
            title="About Me - Tomintech"
            description="Learn about Ayotomiwa Oladotun, a Web3 growth strategist and python developer."
        />
        <style>
            main {
                width: 90%;
                max-width: 800px;
                margin: auto;
                padding: 4rem 0;
            }
            .about-grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 4rem;
            }
            @media (min-width: 768px) {
                .about-grid {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
                }
            }
            .sidebar h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
                padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
            .sidebar ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .sidebar li {
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }
            .main-content h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }
            .main-content .tagline {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                color: #4a5568;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }
            .main-content h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
                margin-top: 3rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }
            .main-content p, .main-content li {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                line-height: 1.7;
            }
            .cv-link {
                 display: inline-block;
                 margin-top: 1rem;
                 padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
                 border-radius: 8px;
                 text-decoration: none;
                 font-weight: 600;
                 background-color: #2d3748;
                 color: white;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <div class="about-grid">
                <aside class="sidebar">
                    <img src="/images/my pro picture.png" alt="Ayotomiwa Oladotun" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 2rem;" />
                    <h2>Key Competencies</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Blockchain and data:</strong> python, web3.py, SQL, on-chain nalysis</li>
                        <li><strong>Strategy:</strong> content lifecycle, SEO audits, keyword research</li>
                        <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> google analytics, ahrefs, n8n, webflow</li>
                        <li><strong>Interpersonal:</strong> collaboration, storytelling, problem-solving</li>
                    </ul>
                     <a href="ayotomiwa crypto analyst.pdf" class="cv-link" download>Download Full CV</a>
                </aside>
                <section class="main-content">
                    <h1>Ayotomiwa Oladotun</h1>
                    <p class="tagline">Web3 marketer and python developer</p>
                    
                    <h2>From strategy to stack</h2>
                    <p>It started with a simple thought: "How does this actually work?" That question took me from a 5-year career in content marketing deep into the engine room of technology. I wasn't satisfied just planning the strategy; I needed to build the tools that execute it.</p>
                    <p>This curiosity led me to build my own smart contract monitoring dashboard from scratch, forcing me to master everything from Python listeners and Flask servers to dynamic frontends that bring live blockchain data to life. This wasn't a distraction; it was an upgrade. Understanding the technical architecture from the inside out has given me a level of insight into Web3 products that I never had before.</p>

                    <h2>Building with AI and Automation</h2>
                    <p>At the same time, I became obsessed with efficiency. This led me to the world of AI Agents and automation platforms like n8n, where I build practical tools to make systems smarter. From a YouTube script writer that pulls from trending topics to a Reddit ad generator that turns customer pain points into comic strips, I build systems that work for you.</p>

                    <h2>What this means for you</h2>
                    <p>I bridge the gap between strategy and execution. When you work with me, you get more than a marketerâ€”you get a technical partner who understands how to build the solutions your growth depends on.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
